# Deployment Checklist

## Pre-Deployment
- All tests pass
- ESLint passes (no errors)
- Bundle size checked with Next DevTools MCP
- Environment variables verified with Vercel MCP
- Dependencies audited with NPM MCP

## Deploy Process
- Deploy to preview first
- Test critical functionality
- Monitor for errors
- Deploy to production

## Post-Deployment
- Check deployment logs
- Monitor error rates
- Verify key user flows
- Be ready to rollback
